<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 17 日星期三 09:17:13 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Putin, Raisi Sign Agreement on Construction of $1.6Bln Rasht-Astara Railway]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110415004" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105726/10/1057261037_0:0:2048:1365_1440x900_80_0_1_2771944fae14ff9bd5ddf3fb7f01cc59.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1057261036" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/putin-raisi-sign-agreement-on-construction-of-16bln-rasht-astara-railway-1110415004.html?share-img=1057261036"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Sergey Subbotin /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">火车从 Yandyki-Olya 铁路开始运营，穿越阿斯特拉罕地区。它是连接俄罗斯与伊朗、印度和东南亚的南北跨国运输走廊的一部分（文件）</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Train operation starting on the Yandyki-Olya railroad stretch, crossing the Astrakhan Region. It is part of the North-South transnational transport corridor, which will link Russia with Iran, India and Southeast Asia (File) - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="火车从 Yandyki-Olya 铁路开始运营，穿越阿斯特拉罕地区。它是连接俄罗斯与伊朗、印度和东南亚的南北跨国运输走廊的一部分（文件）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105726/10/1057261037_0:107:2048:1259_1920x0_80_0_0_3f124a4443d6e258f0721be800d754eb.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105726/10/1057261037_0:107:2048:1259_640x0_80_0_0_3f06f0e9d94e43790152484bd7191de6.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105726/10/1057261037_0:107:2048:1259_1280x0_80_0_0_854740ac861184248f5a57cb0bd74b82.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105726/10/1057261037_0:107:2048:1259_1920x0_80_0_0_3f124a4443d6e258f0721be800d754eb.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Sergey Subbotin /</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周三表示，伊朗拉什特-阿斯塔拉铁路的开通将使全球交通流量多样化，这种运输将具有竞争优势。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">普京与伊朗总统易卜拉欣·雷西通过视频连线参加了铁路建设协议的签署仪式，该铁路是国际南北运输走廊的一部分。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">普京说：“我想强调的是，拉什特-阿斯塔拉铁路将成为其中一部分的独特的南北运输走廊将有助于显着多样化全球交通流量。新走廊沿线的运输将具有显着的竞争优势。”在仪式上。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110415004" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/putin-raisi-sign-agreement-on-construction-of-16bln-rasht-astara-railway-1110415004.html?share-block=1110415006" data-title="&quot;I would like to emphasize that the unique North-South transport corridor, of which the Rasht-Astara railway will become a part, will help to significantly diversify global traffic flows. Transportation along the new corridor will have significant competitive advantages,&quot; Putin said at the ceremony. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">普京补充说，莫斯科希望尽快签署俄罗斯、伊朗和阿塞拜疆关于发展铁路和货运合作的协议。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 09:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/putin-raisi-sign-agreement-on-construction-of-16bln-rasht-astara-railway-1110415004.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/putin-raisi-sign-agreement-on-construction-of-16bln-rasht-astara-railway-1110415004.html<category>经济</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>易卜拉欣·雷西</category><category>拉什特-阿斯塔拉铁路</category><category>国际南北运输走廊 (INSTC) </category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Paris Court of Appeal Upholds Ex-Leader Sarkozy's Sentence in 'Wiretapping Case' - Reports]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110414478" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103491/53/1034915339_0:0:1024:683_1440x900_80_0_1_be95cbe0a009c5aa5a689c8ad2142166.jpg?source-sid=flickr" data-photoview-image-id="1034915338" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/paris-court-of-appeal-upholds-ex-leader-sarkozys-sentence-in-wiretapping-case---reports-1110414478.html?share-i