an></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据巴黎（人造卫星）网报道：据媒体周三报道，巴黎上诉法院在“窃听案”中维持对法国前总统尼古拉·萨科齐 (Nicolas Sarkozy) 三年徒刑的判决，其中两人被缓期执行。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据美国新闻社报道，这位前总统被判犯有腐败和以权谋私罪，并补充说，他的律师蒂埃里·赫尔佐格 (Thierry Herzog) 和前法官吉尔伯特·阿齐伯特 (Gilbert Azibert) 都收到了类似的刑期。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">法院还裁定，萨科齐将不会在监狱服刑剩下的一年，而是在家里戴着电子手环服刑。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 08:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/paris-court-of-appeal-upholds-ex-leader-sarkoozys-sentence-in-wiretapping-case---reports-1110414478.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/paris-court-of-appeal-upholds-ex-leader-sarkoozys-sentence-in-wiretapping-case---reports-1110414478.html<category>世界</category><category>法国</category><category>尼古拉萨科齐</category><category>窃听</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Denmark Touts 'Pragmatic Idealism' as New Foreign Policy Strategy]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110412704" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104241/59/1042415944_0:0:3669:2406_1440x900_80_0_1_bcd2f095afc92a8af4fd95702da2954a.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1042415943" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/denmark-touts-pragmatic-idealism-as-new-foreign-policy-strategy-1110412704.html?share-img=1042415943"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Jens Nørgaard Larsen / SCANPIX DENMARK</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">欧洲国旗和丹麦国旗在哥本哈根的一辆公共汽车上飘扬（文件）</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="European flag and a Danish flag flying on a bus in Copenhagen (File) - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="哥本哈根公交车上飘扬的欧洲国旗和丹麦国旗（资料图）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104241/59/1042415944_0:280:3669:2344_1920x0_80_0_0_98c4543a8c08f4454f9e33e4bad93dc6.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104241/59/1042415944_0:280:3669:2344_640x0_80_0_0_5cb7d48c8d1c14764d41be1f4aee8ecc.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104241/59/1042415944_0:280:3669:2344_1280x0_80_0_0_21086fc40294f95d2a19aa71afb5ecd6.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/104241/59/1042415944_0:280:3669:2344_1920x0_80_0_0_98c4543a8c08f4454f9e33e4bad93dc6.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / Jens Nørgaard Larsen / SCANPIX 丹麦</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊戈尔·库兹涅佐夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_kuznetsov_igor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">新战略涉及“少说教，多倾听”，取代了之前的“基于价值观”的方法，被描述为承认西方正在输给中国和俄罗斯这一事实。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">丹麦外交部长拉尔斯·洛克·拉斯穆森介绍了政府的新外交和安全政策战略，该战略制定了丹麦将如何在全球竞争日益激烈的更加动荡和不可预测的世界中前行的一般原则。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">标榜为“<strong>务实理想主义</strong>”的战略取代了之前的“<strong>基于价值观</strong>”的方法，并被吹捧为世界上第一个反映乌克兰持续冲突的方法。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">正如拉斯穆森自己所说的那样，暗示着一种更现实的世界观：“<strong>我们必须按照世界的实际方式与世界联系，而不是按照我们希望的方式</strong>。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">简而言之，新方法涉及在丹麦与世界其他地区的外联活动中“<strong>少说教，多倾听</strong>”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我们必须相信，我们的价值观比其他地方的价值观更正确，可以提供更好的生活。但是，我们绝不能成为传教士。我们不会冒险把整个世界都放在原地，”拉斯穆森补充道。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110412704" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/denmark-touts-pragmatic-idealism-as-new-foreign-policy-strategy-1110412704.html?share-block=1110412709" data-title="&amp;quot;We must believe that our values are more correct and provide a better life than those you have elsewhere. However, we must not become missionaries. We are not venturing out to put the whole world in its place,&amp;quot; Rasmussen added."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">尽管丹麦打算继续促进平等和打击腐败等事情，但在正式访问期间不一定要把它放在首位。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我们还必须提供其他东西。因为如果我们只带着这些东西去非洲，我们会听到非洲领导人说‘好吧，我们需要水、基础设施和可以提供就业机会的东西。实际上有一些中国人站在那里并提供这一切，那么你就不能给我们讲道吗？”，这位丹麦高级外交官说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110412704" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/denmark-touts-pragmatic-idealism-as-new-foreign-policy-strategy-1110412704.html?share-block=1110412711" data-title="&amp;quot;We must also offer something else. Because if we go to Africa with only that in our bag, we will hear African leaders say &amp;#x27;Well, we need water, infrastructure and something that can provide jobs. And there are actually some Chinese standing there and offering it all, so couldn&amp;#x27;t you just spare us your sermon?,&amp;#x27;&amp;quot; the Danish top diplomat said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">早些时候，拉斯穆森本人将新战略描述为承认西方正在输给中国和俄罗斯这一事实。新的政治蓝图以三个总体外交政策优先事项为中心。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">首先，鉴于乌克兰的持续冲突，更加关注丹麦和欧洲的安全。其次，需要加强全球伙伴关系和联盟。第三，在供应链、能源、关键基础设施等方面建设一个更强大、更有弹性的社会。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在更具体的层面上，丹麦承诺继续支持<u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230426/which-countries-are-sending-weapons-to-ukraine-1109854081.html">基辅政权的军队</a></u>和乌克兰的欧洲一体化，加强<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230422/denmark-withdraws-military-from-syria-iraq-to-combat-threats-near-countrys-borders-1109766614.html"><u>自身的国防</u></a>和安全，为<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230505/denmark-to-spend-billions-to-plug-holes-in-defense-meet-nato-demands-1110110013.html">北约的威慑目标</a>做出贡献，支持欧盟东部和西巴尔干地区的邻国，加强与世界的接触，在全球范围内建立新的联盟和平等伙伴关系，同时扩大丹麦在绿色经济、技术、健康和其他领域的优势地位。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">今年春天早些时候，丹麦宣布计划在未来 10 年内投资 380 亿丹麦克朗（56 亿美元）实现国防现代化，以纠正“错误的政治决策”造成的管理不善和疏忽，并实现北约的开支目标。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，由于北欧国家人员严重短缺，这些计划可能会被放弃。根据最近的报道，目前丹麦陆军的任何一个团都无法集结全部兵力。海军的情况也好不到哪里去，因为它的北极巡逻不得不暂停，以便人手不足的船员可以<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230426/danish-arctic-patrols-so-understaffed-that-ships-stop-for-crews-to-take-nap-1109843389.html" target="_blank">休息或睡觉</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">最后，丹麦的开支狂潮，包括加强本国军队和支持乌克兰的军队，已经耗尽了国库，促使政府采取不受欢迎的措施，例如<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230301/danes-lose-public-holiday-for-first-time-in-250-years-over-military-spending-1107890241.html" target="_blank">取消受欢迎的假期</a>。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 08:26:56 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/denmark-touts-pragmatic-idealism-as-new-foreign-policy-strategy-1110412704.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/denmark-touts-pragmatic-idealism-as-new-foreign-policy-strategy-1110412704.html<category>世界</category><category>拉斯·洛克·拉斯穆森</category><category>丹麦</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>西方</category><category>北约</category><category>欧盟 (EU)</category><category>对外政策</category><category>外交</category><category>价值观</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Mystic Tremors in Baltic Sea Linked to Fighter Jets Breaking Sound Barrier]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110412515" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/0d/1091488826_0:0:2410:1260_1440x900_80_0_1_7f3a4e4d5587b7458d5ba6f549104fef.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1091488822" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/mystic-tremors-in-baltic-sea-linked-to-fighter-jets-breaking-sound-barrier-1110412515.html?share-img=1091488822"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Johan Nilsson / Baltic Ystad</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">波罗的海</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Baltic Sea - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="波罗的海" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/0d/1091488826_170:0:2410:1260_1920x0_80_0_0_8ce3b0941c7fc8ec08a695741e92fd1d.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/0d/1091488826_170:0:2410:1260_640x0_80_0_0_023c17cef831db208dca25cce670639a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/0d/1091488826_170:0:2410:1260_1280x0_80_0_0_af3e4eb00c0c45b22c275c59c090dee4.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/0d/1091488826_170:0:2410:1260_1920x0_80_0_0_8ce3b0941c7fc8ec08a695741e92fd1d.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Johan Nilsson / Baltic Ystad </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊戈尔·库兹涅佐夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_kuznetsov_igor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">所谓的音爆是一种与物体以超过音速的速度在空气中传播所产生的冲击波有关的声音。对人耳来说，它听起来类似于爆炸或响亮的雷声。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在丹麦博恩霍尔姆岛观察到的同样神秘的震颤和低频声音也让当地人和研究人员感到困惑，在瑞典南部的布莱金厄县和波罗的海奥兰岛也有记录。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">乌普萨拉大学副教授、地震学家 Björn Lund 引用了当地人的“低频声音和震动”的报道，以至于<strong>窗户都在摇晃</strong>。上周末，据说这种现象持续了 10 到 13 秒。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">丹麦和格陵兰地质调查局（GEUS）将地震归因于大气中“<strong>不明来源</strong>”的压力波，为故事增添了更多悬念。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">不过，隆德指出，同样的现象在瑞典每年都会被测量数次，包括斯德哥尔摩群岛，经查明震颤是由战斗机突破音速障碍引起的。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>音爆是一种与物体以高于音速的速度在空气中传播所产生的冲击波相关的声音。音爆产生巨大的声能，在人耳中听起来类似于爆炸或霹雳。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>“这些现象与我们每年在这里看到几次的现象非常相似。所以对我来说，这是最直接的原因，”隆德告诉丹麦媒体。</em></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据隆德的说法，由于逆温现象，音爆可能显得更大声，在这种现象中，地球上方空气层中的一组不同温度会影响声音的传播。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，无论是丹麦人还是瑞典军方都无法证实他们在星期六（即这种现象最后一次发生的那天） <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230505/denmark-to-spend-billions-to-plug-holes-in-defense-meet-nato-demands-1110110013.html" target="_blank">机翼上</a>有战斗机。瑞典<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230223/finland-to-buy-39mln-worth-of-anti-tank-missiles-from-swedens-saab-1107735725.html" target="_blank">武器制造商萨博</a>——根据隆德的说法，在瑞典之前的观察中通常是“罪魁祸首”——也没有承认周六进行了试飞。然而，波兰当局此前曾透露，在该国北部的 Anakonda23 演习期间发生了激烈的军事活动，其中涉及一架战斗机和大炮弹药的实弹射击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">博恩霍尔姆岛（人口 40,000）是波罗的海的一个岩石岛，位于瑞典南部、德国东北部和波兰北部。它距离 2022 年 9 月北溪 1 号和北溪 2 号天然气管道遭到<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/nord-stream-leaks/" target="_blank">破坏的</a>地点特别近。有关国家的当局仍在调查爆炸事件。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">资深记者 Seymour Hersh 随后进行的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230322/blackout-sy-hersh-says-us-germany-coordinated-nyt-false-cover-story-for-nord-stream-bombing-1108696791.html" target="_blank">重磅调查</a>表明，美国和挪威参与了管道袭击；此后，这遭到了拜登政府的多次拒绝。西方媒体反而暗示了一个潜在的亲乌克兰组织在爆炸事件中的作用。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯安全委员会副主席德米特里梅德韦杰夫表示，莫斯科认为这两条管道的爆炸是国际恐怖主义行为，并将继续使用任何可用的法律机制将责任人<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230512/medvedev-russia-using-all-tools-to-punish-those-responsible-for-nord-stream-explosions-1110303849.html" target="_blank">绳之以法</a>。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 07:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/mystic-tremors-in-baltic-sea-linked-to-fighter-jets-breaking-sound-barrier-1110412515.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/mystic-tremors-in-baltic-sea-linked-to-fighter-jets-breaking-sound-barrier-1110412515.html<category>超越政治</category><category>欧洲</category><category>西摩·赫什</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>瑞典</category><category>波罗的海</category><category>萨博</category><category>北溪 2</category><category>北溪</category><category>战斗机</category><category>丹麦</category><category>消息</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Group of Countries Led by Poland Secretly Urging Zelensky to End Conflict - Hersh]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110414173" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:0:2395:1635_1440x900_80_0_1_740ea2df329b355dd9824f5d55571f00.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1097069891" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/group-of-countries-led-by-poland-secretly-urging-zelensky-to-end-conflict---hersh-1110414173.html?share-img=1097069891"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / 乌克兰总统新闻办公室</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">乌克兰总统 Volodymyr Zelensky</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky  - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="乌克兰总统泽连斯基" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1920x0_80_0_0_404c2bf28b0ef25f831626437dc6dc03.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_640x0_80_0_0_862c04ecd6632409316f24d999722539.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1280x0_80_0_0_28989948db8edeb4d5d73d84013ee941.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/07/07/1097069908_0:117:2395:1464_1920x0_80_0_0_404c2bf28b0ef25f831626437dc6dc03.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / 乌克兰总统新闻办公室</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：普利策奖获得者美国调查记者西摩赫什周三表示，以波兰为首的东欧盟友正在秘密敦促乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔泽连斯基结束乌克兰冲突，甚至辞职，但乌克兰领导人拒绝这样做. </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Hersh 在他的 Substack 页面上提到了以波兰为首的国家集团“敦促 Zelensky 找到结束敌对行动的方法”。他们强调，他应该“甚至在必要时辞职——并让重建国家的进程开始”来结束冲突。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位调查记者引用了美国情报界成员秘密报告的信息，其中包括匈牙利、立陶宛、爱沙尼亚和拉脱维亚等国。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “根据中央情报局内部已知的截获和其他数据，泽伦斯基没有让步，但他开始失去邻居的私人支持，”赫什补充说。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 07:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/group-of-countries-led-by-poland-secretly-urging-zelensky-to-end-conflict---hersh-1110414173.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/group-of-countries-led-by-poland-secretly-urging-zelensky-to-end-conflict---hersh-1110414173.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>沃洛德米尔·泽伦斯基</category><category>西摩·赫什</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Photos: Kim Jong-un Inspects Work on North Korea's First Reconnaissance Satellite]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110413070" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0a/1108269493_0:0:900:596_1440x900_80_0_1_8468ce2baaf0138f633182ee681808d3.jpg?source-sid=" data-photoview-image-id="1108269474" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/kim-inspects-work-on-north-koreas-first-reconnaissance-satellite-1110413070.html?share-img=1108269474"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="http://www.kcna.kp/en/media/photo/q/43d5997f6109c95ebdd0c10d4d4f562f5c0a63adef93ab237d90a24210565ede.kcmsf" title="朝中社">KCNA</a></span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2023 年 3 月 9 日，朝鲜领导人金正恩、人民军高层和金的女儿在南浦观看火箭炮演习。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="" alt="DPRK leader Kim Jong Un, KPA brass, and Kim's daughter watch a rocket artillery drill in Nampo on March 9, 2023. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="2023 年 3 月 9 日，朝鲜领导人金正恩、人民军高层和金正恩的女儿在南浦观看火箭炮演习。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0a/1108269493_0:60:900:566_1920x0_80_0_0_53d371719a6a91e2b91f2d8a40d87585.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0a/1108269493_0:60:900:566_640x0_80_0_0_b0c7f51b4528c542090dd4cb80e28921.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0a/1108269493_0:60:900:566_1280x0_80_0_0_af117668e628dc373d16099b72109fab.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0a/1108269493_0:60:900:566_1920x0_80_0_0_53d371719a6a91e2b91f2d8a40d87585.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="http://www.kcna.kp/en/media/photo/q/43d5997f6109c95ebdd0c10d4d4f562f5c0a63adef93ab237d90a24210565ede.kcmsf" title="朝中社">朝中社</a></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：据朝鲜官方通讯社周三报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩视察了朝鲜首颗旨在威慑美国和韩国的军事侦察卫星的发射准备工作。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “他[金]检查了经过最后总装检查和空间环境测试后准备装载的军事侦察一号卫星。他高度赞赏筹委会在过程中以负责任的方式履行其职责和作用开展大幅发展国家军事技术的重要工作，”媒体报道。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报道称，这位朝鲜领导人周二当场发表讲话，强调拥有这样一颗卫星的重要性，尤其是考虑到华盛顿和首尔对平壤采取的“对抗行动”。国营新机构援引金正恩的话说，朝鲜“将行使其主权和正当的自卫权，以威慑他们并保卫国家”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告称，朝鲜领导人列出了该国在卫星发射后需要实现的国防和太空研究目标，并为委员会的进一步行动计划开了绿灯。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “成功发射军事侦察卫星，是当前国家安全环境的迫切要求，是正确贯彻党和政府把加强国防建设放在第一位的方针政策的过程，同时，在发展国家的太空军事和科学技术方面取得了明显的进步，”新闻社援引金正恩的话说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 4 月，朝鲜领导人下令<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230419/north-korea-to-launch-military-satellite-to-target-enemies-with-nuclear-missiles-1109662899.html" target="_blank">按计划发射</a>已经完成的该国第一颗军事侦察卫星。据朝中社报道，在发射前，该卫星计划进行总装检查和空间环境测试。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 06:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/kim-inspects-work-on-north-koreas-first-reconnaissance-satellite-1110413070.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/kim-inspects-work-on-north-koreas-first-reconnaissance-satellite-1110413070.html<category>亚洲</category><category>北朝鲜</category><category>金正恩</category><category>威慑</category></item></channel></rss>